 is from lies, falsehood, vain talk, and swearing.\u201d Source: Mus\u0323annaf Ibn Abi\u0304 Shaybah 8882 \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0627\u0644\u0634\u0651\u064e\u0639\u0652\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0651\u0650 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0639\u064f\u0645\u064e\u0631\u064f \u0631\u064e\u0636\u0650\u064a\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652\u0647\u064f \u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0633\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0635\u0651\u0650\u064a\u064e\u0627\u0645\u064f \u0645\u0650\u0646\u0652 \u0627\u0644\u0637\u0651\u064e\u0639\u064e\u0627\u0645\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0627\u0644\u0634\u0651\u064e\u0631\u064e\u0627\u0628\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":5913,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/09\/04\/worst-muslims-arrogant\/","url_meta":{"origin":34999,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Arrogance: Worst Muslims brag, boast, speak too much","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 4, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe worst of my nation are the garrulous, the braggarts,\u00a0and the pompous. The best of my nation are those with the best character.\u201d Source: al-Adab al-Mufrad lil-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 1308 Grade: Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0647\u064f\u0631\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u064e\u0651\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0650\u0651\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":979,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2011\/08\/06\/true-fasting-leave-bad-words\/","url_meta":{"origin":34999,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Sawm: True fasting is leaving sins, bad words","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 6, 2011","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \"Whoever does not leave evil words and deeds while fasting, Allah does not need him to leave food and drink.\" Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 1903 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Bukhari \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0647\u064f\u0631\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":26031,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2018\/03\/06\/sufyan-sabr-food-water\/","url_meta":{"origin":34999,"position":4},"title":"Sufyan on Sabr: Believers need patience like food and water","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 6, 2018","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Humaydi reported: Sufyan al-Thawri, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cThe believer is in need of patience just as he is in need of food and drink.\u201d Source: al-S\u0323abr li-Ibn Abi\u0304 Dunya\u0304 84 \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u062d\u064f\u0645\u064e\u064a\u0652\u062f\u0650\u064a\u0651\u0650 \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0633\u064f\u0641\u0652\u064a\u064e\u0627\u0646\u064e \u0627\u0644\u062b\u0651\u064e\u0648\